entries.title_d: Transfer cargo from a Nym contact in the Lok System to a Hutt Transport in the Dantooine System
entries.title: Lok System: Transport Goods Between Systems
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Hutt Transport: < \#pcontrast1 I have a bit of CorSec heat on me at the moment, I need you to complete this delivery for me across the System.  The contact knows to expect you. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel here to deliver the cargo
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: Travel here to recieve the cargo from the Nym contact
entries.quest_location_d: A trade route between the Lok and Dantooine Systems
entries.quest_dock2_d: Use the /dock command to transfer the cargo
entries.quest_dock1_d: Use the /dock command to recieve the cargo
entries.hello_p: Hey there, we got the package for Jabba.  Move into position for docking.
entries.hello_d: We are going to get a little fancy with you, get in to dock and we can discues it further.
entries.found_loc_p: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Coordinates locked in for rendezvous point. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc_d: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Coordinates locked in for rendezvous point. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.docking_complete_pickup: The docking is complete, starting delivery.  Take the cargo to Dantooine System, we will update you from there.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: We have another package for you to deliver, exchanging cargo now.
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile activity has ceased. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated rendezvous waypoint reached. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_delivery: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Designated rendezvous waypoint reached. \#pcontrast3 >
